                <head>No. 650.</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#center">[Cable message, received at
                            <placeName>Washington</placeName>
                        <date calendar="gregorian" when="1880-07-23">July 23, 1880—6.55
                        p.m</date>.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p rend="flushleft">To Secretary <hi rend="smallcaps">Evarts</hi>, <hi rend="italic"
                        >Washington:</hi>
                </p>
                <p>Commission liquidation finished and adjourned: all powers adhered.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>FARMAN.</signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
